reviewText: Morrison is indeed a wizard on any musical instrument he touches. He has it all on trumpet and trombone, and he's pretty accomplished on piano as well. The video was well done, but it might have come off better if there'd been a little more performance. Nine on a scale of ten.  Bill Cox

James Morrison is an incredible musician and it was rewarding to learn something about this Aussie and his background. If I had a criticism of this video it would be that I wished they had show more of his playing. After all, he is one of the best musicians in the world. However, I was too delighted to learn more about this world-class talent to complain.
